<template>
    <section>

</template>

<script>
import localApiClient from "../../services/Api";

export default {
    data() {
        return {
            fees: null
        }
    },
    created() {
        localApiClient.get('/fee/all-fees').then((response) => {
            console.log(response.data);
            this.fees = response.data;
        }).catch((error) => console.log(error));
    }
}
</script>
